    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Pinball machines, game consoles, jukeboxes and dance floors, a mini-bar, a home theater, a comfortable couch, or whatever else - the kinds of personal touches that turn an apartment into a home. Whatever it is, it's top of the line, likely custom-ordered by the Afterlife at your request. Each purchase of the morale boost reduces the rent cost of Floor 4 by 1/4th an Eagle (rounded down) or 50eb.</p><p>Multiple installations stack across the entire HQ, and offer the bonuses outlined in the No Place Like Home DLC, page 5. Every other installation (installation 2, 4, 6, etc.) still costs HQ IP, but does not require a room slot.</p>"
